  "title": "Loomy Comforting Mung-bean-sproutsukju Pilaf",
  "description": "A glassy-jelly, sour comfort dish featuring mung-bean sprout sukju in a dairy-free comforting Ukrainian rice pilaf, perfect for lunch.",
