  "instructions": [
    "Rinse rice and soak in water for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Drain and transfer to a pot with the soaked water, add lemon-lime soda, salt, and cover. Bring to boil then reduce heat to low and simmer until liquid is absorbed, about 25-30 minutes.",
    "In another pan, warm olive oil over medium heat. Add onion and garlic, sauté until softened.",
    "Fold in mung-bean sproutsukju, stir to combine with rice mixture. Adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Garnish with fresh dill before serving."
